<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA67">
<l>āṅku malaruṅ kuviyumā luntivā</l>
<l>yōṅku kamalatti ṉoṇpō – tāṅkait</l>
<l>tikiri cuṭareṉṟum veṇcaṅkam vāṉiṟ</l>
<l>pakaru matiyeṉṟum pārttu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In the navel of Māl, where there are blossoms heaped,</l>
<l>there is a bright bud of a high lotus – peering</l>
<l>at the discus in [his] hand, thinking [it] the sun,</l>
<l>[and] at the white conch, thinking [it] the moon that shines in the sky.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
